YOUR EX-WIFE AND
DAUGHTER DOWN HERE

1924
01:28:19,000 --> 01:28:21,000
UNDER FALSE PRETENSES.

1925
01:28:21,000 --> 01:28:24,000
IF THERE WAS EVER A TIME
