UPSET, HONEY.

1932
01:28:38,000 --> 01:28:40,000
OH, JUST STOP IT!

1933
01:28:40,000 --> 01:28:42,000
BOTH OF YOU.

1934
01:28:42,000 --> 01:28:44,000
I'M TIRED TO DEATH
OF JESSE MORAN,

1935
01:28:44,000 --> 01:28:47,000
AND I'M TIRED
OF THE TWO OF YOU.

1936
01:28:47,000 --> 01:28:48,000
