AND MAGGIE ALWAYS
TRYING TO PATCH,
PATCH, PATCH

1939
01:28:54,000 --> 01:28:56,000
SOMETHING THAT'S
BEYOND FIXING.

1940
01:28:58,000 --> 01:29:00,000
WELL, YOU KNOW
WHAT'S WRONG?

1941
01:29:00,000 --> 01:29:02,000
WE'RE ALL JUST
TIRED AND HUNGRY.

1942
01:29:02,000 --> 01:29:04,000
WE'LL ALL FEEL BETTER

1943
