I PROMISE.

1946
01:29:10,000 --> 01:29:11,000
YOU'LL SEE.

1947
01:29:11,000 --> 01:29:13,000
EVERYTHING'S READY
BACK THERE.

1948
01:29:13,000 --> 01:29:16,000
I'LL JUST GO
AND MAKE SURE
IT ISN'T BURNING.

1949
01:29:37,000 --> 01:29:39,000
LEROY!

1950
